lyrics:
[verse]
Pedaling hard through the desert sand
In Dubai's race, we take a bold stand
Adrenaline pumping, hearts beating fast
We conquer the roads, our strength unsurpassed

[chorus]
Dubai, oh Dubai, where champions shine bright
With the wind as our guide, we're soaring in flight
Through the heat and the sun, we'll never back down
In this road cycling race, we wear victory's crown
